h there are insinuations of Serbian involvement by NGOs.\"\nThe only party taking an dissenting was opposition Democratic Party. Du\u0161an Petrovi\u0107 told journalists that \"it is not true that NGOs are leading anti-Serbian campaign ... I don't think that any action aimed at bringing criminals to justice is negative in any way.\""}
